they look like on the inside.

36
00:01:16.728 --> 00:01:17.767
Fuck!
Stop!

37
00:01:17.809 --> 00:01:18.848
Fuckin' piece of shit!
Okay. stop it!

38
00:01:18.890 --> 00:01:21.011
Stop! Hey!
Kristi. hey. hey! Stop!

39
00:01:21.053 --> 00:01:22.332
KENNY: You really think
injecting them

40
