we can start as--
No. no. no. no. no.

97
00:06:01.052 --> 00:06:03.054
Not the antenna.
I'm talking about this.

98
00:06:04.376 --> 00:06:07.176
Let's say this is
one real big experiment.

99
00:06:07.218 --> 00:06:08.578
