someone on the inside.

135
00:07:44.315 --> 00:07:46.275
Ah. you can't just start
throwing around accusations...

136
00:07:46.317 --> 00:07:48.440
I'm not saying accuse.
I just...

137
00:07:49.761 --> 00:07:52.482
