Boyd. Donna. Father Khatri.

140
00:07:59.090 --> 00:08:00.249
Father who?

141
00:08:00.291 --> 00:08:02.371
Khatri.
He died.

142
00:08:02.413 --> 00:08:04.574
That night they got
into the Colony House.

143
00:08:04.616 --> 00:08:05.655
Well. did you see it?

144
00:08:05.697 --> 00:08:06.896
