149
00:08:15.827 --> 00:08:17.827
Right.

150
00:08:17.869 --> 00:08:20.830
And of all the people that
died since you've been here.

151
00:08:20.872 --> 00:08:23.314
how many times have you
actually seen it happen?

152
00:08:24.155 --> 00:08:26.155
