to see if that shit was real.

166
00:08:56.548 --> 00:08:58.588
Have you seen one ounce
of proof that anyone here
has actually...

167
00:08:58.630 --> 00:08:59.749
Nathan.

168
00:08:59.791 --> 00:09:01.070
What?

169
