Nowhere for me to go.

213
00:11:00.912 --> 00:11:05.436
Okay. Good. now we're talking
about problems we can fix.

214
00:11:10.281 --> 00:11:11.841
Down there.

215
00:11:11.883 --> 00:11:13.362
That's where
I saw your symbol.

216
00:11:13.404 --> 00:11:15.406
and it's...

217
